item.title: CVE-2020-7822|2024-09-16T16:49:02.141Z -- humantalk%20co%2Cltd -- daviewindy
item.description: DaviewIndy has a Heap-based overflow vulnerability, triggered when the user opens a malformed image file that is mishandled by Daview.exe. Attackers could exploit this and arbitrary code execution.
